com.ekito.simpleKML.model

Class ColorStyle

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ekito.simpleKML.model.Object
      • com.ekito.simpleKML.model.ColorStyle
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    BalloonStyle, IconStyle, LabelStyle, LineStyle, ListStyle, PolyStyle

    public abstract class ColorStyle
extends Object
    This is an abstract element and cannot be used directly in a KML file. It provides elements for specifying the color and color mode of extended style types.
